Setting Hugo Website &amp; Host on Github Quick Usage Instructions  Edit/add new content, this will automatically create new article in &ldquo;content&rdquo; directory.
hugo new &lt;subdirectory_name&gt;/&lt;articlename.extension&gt;
Ex. hugo new posts/new_post.md Push everything from project root &ldquo;hugoWebsite&rdquo; to Github git status git add . git commit -m &quot;added new article&quot; git push origin main Render the content to &ldquo;public&rdquo; directory hugo -D Go to &ldquo;public&rdquo; directory and commit everything to GitHub cd public
